description: A category based launcher LukeLauncher is a fast, minimal, categorie based home screen replacement. ------------------------------------------------- LukeLauncher – Features ------------------------------------------------- • Apps are managed in categories • Suitable for left and right handers • Notifications are supported • Widgets are supported • Supports Tablets (Horizontal and vertical alignment possible) • Quick search function • Iconpacks can be used • Multilingual (English, German, Spanish and Czech) … and much much more! Website: https://lukelauncher.de
